INSERT INTO sm_news VALUES("5","INFINITY TECHNOLOGY INT. LTD.","6","1","public/uploads/news/0492e4cbf1fa4427f4046bb596f189b9.jpg","","<p>Since two decades, in a staple sector like Information Technology there hasn&rsquo;t been so many houses that have been contributing or have accommodated over 200 IT professionals like Infinity Technology International Limited in Bangladesh. 24 years ago a group of graduates from USA, Australia, Bangladesh and family member of renowned &lsquo;freedom fighters&rsquo; dreamed of a country where people will use Information Technology for Banking developed by Infinity Technology Int. Ltd. Of Bangladesh.</p>","2021-05-09","5","2021-09-11 01:41:02","2021-09-15 07:45:14","2","1","1","1","1");
INSERT INTO sm_news VALUES("13","APPLY NOW","","","public/uploads/news/stu-c7d30864c27fbcfe78695a73e93bb09e.jpg","","<p>Teaching and learning go hand in hand. Faculty training and development has been a high priority for us. Scholastica is the first school that has undertaken an initiative to certify all teachers. We have engaged a professional training organization, SPEED, to conduct formal teacher training courses for our faculty&mdash;a one-year teaching skills course offered by Cambridge International Examinations.</p>","2021-09-01","","2021-09-15 07:57:31","2021-09-15 07:57:31","4","1","1","1","1");
INSERT INTO sm_news VALUES("14","Qualifications","","","public/uploads/news/stu-c00775e5a9f92858369bd43642295268.jpg","","<h3>We are proud of our faculty, who work hard to challenge, teach and inspire our students. Our teachers are typically graduate or post-graduate degree holders in their respective subjects from well-reputed institutions. A number of our teachers have an educational background in teaching with degrees such as M.Ed or B.Ed.</h3>","2021-09-29","","2021-09-15 07:58:33","2021-09-15 07:58:33","5","1","1","1","1");
INSERT INTO sm_news VALUES("15","Faculty Search","","","public/uploads/news/stu-4eebffc223660c9afb6081af19caf1a3.jpg","","<p>Teachers are some of the busiest educational professionals in the country! We are committed to excellence and work hard to deliver our best to our students. High standards are maintained through intensive and comprehensive training programs. Close monitoring and supervision is provided to help teachers implement modern teaching methods.</p>","2021-10-07","","2021-09-15 07:59:30","2021-09-15 07:59:30","2","1","1","1","1");
